XUL::App's TODO:
* Add support for the --profile option, like this:
    $ xulapp debug --profile dev3 foo.xul
 It will also create a profile if it doesn't exist.
 It will also checks prefs.js to see whether the necessary variables have been set or not. If not, it will set those config vars automatically.

